text: Chloe Frances Dykstra (born September 15, 1988) is an American model and actress. She produced and co-hosted the internet web series Just Cos for Nerdist Industries' YouTube channel. She is a cast member in Syfy's show Heroes of Cosplay. She is also a freelance game journalist for several websites.
